至令中共識驚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"禁止出口non-gmo 大豆到中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"人命同大豆比<br />\n你無病丫嘛？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ff8346d6cceaa565b23bac36f2e76b233892ac","tid":984932,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"軍隊都冇要靠美軍照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f526f57fa84bffe14931001a2cfb9682d667a1","tid":984932,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"死刑?整單血洗唐人街恐怖襲擊咪得囉"},{"pid":"44b5e01b5cb34fc0b2c5687c3a77380585c428ec","tid":984932,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T04:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe0569fed1e08c14ac2e5efff08424cd64512d5","tid":984932,"uid":25643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e5ff8346d6cceaa565b23bac36f2e76b233892ac","tid":984932,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"軍隊都冇要靠美軍照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"咁二戰加拿大嚟香港作戰個班人係咩嘢?"},{"pid":"1ca9692b3899f646368b66b8652a1f7f68bff967","tid":984932,"uid":163801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"加拿大人如果喺其他國家(例如菲律賓)被判死刑, 加拿大政府都會出面要求赦免死刑, 因為加拿大本身反對死刑制度.<br />\n<br />\n當然, 如果人哋唔理佢, 佢哋都冇咩進一步行動. 可以話出吓面講句嘢, 俾自己人睇吓佢哋做過嘢出過聲. 你估好似支那香港政府咩.<br />\n<br />\n講到加拿大求支那真係吹到咁大... 加拿大最驚係你唔處決個毒犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae82d701f27f2a369c48f4cbc5f264557858d44f","tid":984932,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgX5ZXy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgX5ZXy.jpg&h=1bf57e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拿著王八蛋簽署的和約興高采烈的樣子"},{"pid":"65e0341fc8523abf326ccec3eb26a17b1a850334","tid":984932,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"有論者表示，加國如果介入引渡申請，<span style=\"color: red;\">私下警告孟晚舟不要途經溫哥華，那麼渥太華就能避免許多麻煩</span>，而孟晚舟也不會在機場被捕。<br />\n<br />\n根本無可能<br />\n慢慢周唔上飛機點知佢會去溫哥華轉機<br />\n一定係佢check in咗由航空公司通知美國有通緝犯上咗飛機<br />\n然後美國司法部通知溫哥華準備封艇拉人<br />\n成件事加拿大好被動<br />\n只可以話俾美國擺咗上枱"}]}